    <p>{`Of course there are cases where the user can only be helped by contacting us (i.e. bugs, problems with Early Access features, or account-specific issues), so our contact info will remain readily accessible on the marketing site and knowledge base, and we'll continue to offer live chat in the product, but we don't want to encourage people reading the KB to just contact us without trying anything themselves first.`}</p>
