    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Quality - MP4 videos will generally be of higher quality than an animated GIF`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`File size - MP4 videos are smaller in size, especially for longer clips, so users won't have to wait as long for page content to load`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Performance - most computers have decent hardware video acceleration, but GIFs can't use hardware acceleration and take quite a bit of CPU time instead, meaning even modern computers may cry if we use them`}</li>
